title: SCPUI Test Mod
description:
This is a proof-of-concept mod that allows easy testing of the new HD interface being built by m!m and mjn.mixael.

This version replaces the following screens...

-pilot select
-barracks
-options
-campaign
-tech room database
-tech room simulator
-tech room cutscenes
-tech room credits
-fiction viewer
-command briefing
-briefing
-ship select
-weapon select
-debriefing
-all dialog popups
